content.rendered:
GNY Tokens

GNY Mainnet utility tokens are the backbone of the GNY Blockchain and will be an integral part of unlocking features and abilities on the GNY Range Report. You can purchase ERC-20 versions of the token on exchanges, then use GNY’s innovative Swapgate to convert them to GNY Mainnet tokens, enabling access to GNY’s ML utility, delegate voting etc.

GNY ERC-20 token contract code: 0xb1f871ae9462f1b2c6826e88a7827e76f86751d4

Learn more about the token and the exchanges listing it: https://www.gny.io/gny-token/

GNY Swapgate

GNY’s Swapgate is built to offer a two-way swap between the GNY Mainnet utility token and the GNY ERC-20 token tradable on exchanges. The Swapgate’s seamless movement between these token formats will eventually facilitate collaborative ML and crypto insights directly unlocked through Metamask and the GNY Mobile Wallet.
